{"tid":240251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭巴士前面對情侶係到含撚","createTime":"2017-05-12T09:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T10:18:34.000Z","uid":35411,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5cb75bde0e5aaea38247c411f497a26d83fdcf","tid":240251,"uid":35411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:36:47.000Z","msg":"一上車佢地就已經慾火焚身咁係咁咀<br />\n我就玩電話唔想望<br />\n點知前面條友突然拎件褸出黎發到我隻腳<br />\n咁我就望下個撚屌做咩大熱天時攞件褸出來<br />\n原來條女訓左係佢大脾<br />\n佢拎黎幫佢擋太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我無理繼續玩電話，<br />\n點知聽到前面又傳來吸啜聲，<br />\n我企係到望佢地做緊咩<br />\n但佢地意亂情迷，旁若無人<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候到站喇，無得同佢講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公眾地方檢點啲喇</span>"},{"pid":"d65b05ef2ee63c26660f460c19656fee99d2695d","tid":240251,"uid":9395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc38d96ce4756c20c4c3ae0c0a51da32180ab17","tid":240251,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"樓主酸到出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0821ad7ded49d33451ca8029a5a1c00aae54af","tid":240251,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"負皮係比樓主既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.最尾個句一定無講（無撚用 因為自己都打緊飛機）<br />\n2.無拍到片 圖都無張 （咁講到佢地咁旁若無人 咁比人影都唔怕架啦 更何況佢地分緊心）"},{"pid":"561c843258adbf9d5a30fae9ac2b4caf13e42fd7","tid":240251,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死毒撚又唔敢講野"},{"pid":"84c0c4c462f9f1aa8a88785d1658626addfce83a","tid":240251,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人 打救 樓主 母親"},{"pid":"280257b4e9a8d20a4242b5ecedbc7c7d95913a63","tid":240251,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/174646_ab400f9d6c05b0c9f33095def6c59372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F174646_ab400f9d6c05b0c9f33095def6c59372.jpg&h=c54a83d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/174647_487457efc7b8493a768ea1d543b8d64f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F174647_487457efc7b8493a768ea1d543b8d64f.jpg&h=64662616&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd83b7ead7062a64fd306fd44a5f7a6c6befead2","tid":240251,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"767bcf9e681c9ea06f0176beea25a005c0d118e2","tid":240251,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"片都無段。。"},{"pid":"c63f386d68c20a0e840b15ca74ad1e5cfa5ee13a","tid":240251,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://na.cx/i/5wt6ts.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5wt6ts.jpg&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6de95436\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/5wt6ts.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都無扯到"},{"pid":"18e4c4cc23420497cbe5833cd9d12fe79140a2b9","tid":240251,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"一對情侶係度含撚🤔"},{"pid":"06b6c73fd7f3d4dc8288a07fdd98d209a7509e57","tid":240251,"uid":76412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><